text: Tiril Bue (born 26 April 1993) is a Norwegian competitive sailor. She qualified for competing in the Laser Radial class at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Norwegian female sailors (sport) Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – Laser Radial Category:Olympic sailors of Norway
